{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-030","title":"误解与沟通","sectionId":"chapter-02","sectionTitle":"日常交际你最强","pageStart":172,"pageEnd":176,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":20,"duplicateEntryCount":16,"pages":[{"number":172,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"30 误解与沟通"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"misunderstand [ˌmɪsʌndəˈstænd]","headword":"misunderstand"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.误解，误会"},{"type":"note","text":"◎misunderstand for误认为…"},{"type":"entry","text":"misunderstanding [ˌmɪsʌndəˈstændɪŋ]","headword":"misunderstanding"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.误解，误会"},{"type":"note","text":"◎cause misunderstanding引起误会"},{"type":"entry","text":"misinterpretation [ˌmɪsɪntɜːprɪˈteɪʃn]","headword":"misinterpretation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.误释"},{"type":"note","text":"◎intentional misinterpretation有意曲解"},{"type":"entry","text":"misread [ˌmɪsˈriːd]","headword":"misread"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.读错；误解"},{"type":"note","text":"◎completely misread完全误解"},{"type":"entry","text":"cultural difference 文化差异","headword":"cultural difference"}]},{"number":173,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"incomprehensible [ɪnˌkɒmprɪˈhensəbl]","headword":"incomprehensible"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.费解的，不可理解的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be incomprehensible to使…费解"},{"type":"entry","text":"confused [kənˈfjuːzd]","headword":"confused"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.困惑的；混淆的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎feel confused感到困惑"},{"type":"entry","text":"be confused with与…混淆","headword":"be confused with"},{"type":"entry","text":"mistrust [ˌmɪsˈtrʌst]","headword":"mistrust"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v. 不信任，怀疑"}]},{"number":174,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"embarrassment [ɪmˈbærəsmənt]","headword":"embarrassment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.尴尬，难堪"},{"type":"note","text":"◎feel embarrassment感到尴尬"},{"type":"entry","text":"explain [ɪkˈspleɪn]","headword":"explain"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.解释，说明"},{"type":"note","text":"◎explain to向…解释"},{"type":"entry","text":"link up 衔接；沟通","headword":"link up"},{"type":"entry","text":"transpire [trænˈspaɪə(r)]","headword":"transpire"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.（指事情、秘密等）公开；发生"},{"type":"entry","text":"contact number联系电话","headword":"contact number"}]},{"number":175,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"clear [klɪə(r)]","headword":"clear"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.清楚的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎crystal clear十分清楚"},{"type":"entry","text":"coherent [kəʊˈhɪərənt]","headword":"coherent"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.连贯的"},{"type":"entry","text":"concise summary 简洁的总结","headword":"concise summary"},{"type":"entry","text":"intelligible speech 清楚的讲话","headword":"intelligible speech"},{"type":"entry","text":"distinct statement 确切的声明","headword":"distinct statement"},{"type":"entry","text":"respondent behaviour 应答行为","headword":"respondent behaviour"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"}]},{"number":176,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：I thought his jokes were funny. （我觉得他的笑话挺逗的。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：No way! They were racist! He offends a lot of people.（一点也"},{"type":"text","text":"不！都是些种族主义的笑话！他冒犯了很多人。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I'd like to explain about the programme.（我来解释一下这个计"},{"type":"text","text":"划。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：OK, go ahead.（好的，请讲。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：So from now on he will be taking over my duties? （那么，从今"},{"type":"text","text":"往后他接我的班？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：No. I'm sorry; maybe I wasn't being clear.（不是的。抱歉，也许"},{"type":"text","text":"我没有说清楚。）"}]}]}